description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Whole Body Circuit ' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The The Meditative Grind vibe means Zone in, lock down, let repetition take over. This is especially good for Those who love a slow burn and rhythmic intensity. The The Disciplined Grind vibe means No excuses, no distractions, just execute. This is especially good for When you want pure focus and efficiency..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Strengthen your whole body and improve your cardio on your Hydrow as Pete leads you through this circuit. 

Max rhythm: 24, Format: EMOM...
